<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">ابن الصلاح:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>تقدمت ترجمته في ج ١ ص ٣٣٠.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
